* import the data
ssc install bcuse, replace
bcuse injury, clear
* For the Stata application we do not need an "id"

*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
* create two state subsets
* Kentucky subset
gen injury_ky = ky==1
* Michigan subset
gen injury_mi = mi==1
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*     A. Kentucky Sample
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Unconditional DiD analysis
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Duration of benefits
regress durat i.highearn i.afchnge i.highearn#i.afchnge if injury_ky==1, robust
 
* Log of duration of benefits
regress ldurat i.highearn i.afchnge i.highearn#i.afchnge if injury_ky==1, robust

